ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[As of 7 Jul 2020, the total number of cases of COVID-19 confirmed in Iran is 245 688, including 11 931 deaths, an increase of 2637 cases and 200 deaths since 6 Jul 2020. The number of daily reported cases and deaths are slowing increasing. According to the media report, 20 out of the 31 provinces are experiencing increases.

Takeaway message (unchanged): Premature lifting of restrictions is taking its toll in Iran as is elsewhere in the world.

A map of Iran showing provinces can be seen at https://www.mapsofworld.com/iran/iran-political-map.html and a HealthMap/ProMED map at https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=7551918,128. - Mod.MPP]

